ing: 1 (15 ounce) can baked beans with pork
des: "This is nice and thick and yummy. Sour cream is also good on this."
ins: Crumble the ground beef into a large skillet or Dutch oven over medium-high heat. Add onion; cook and stir until beef is no longer pink. Drain off grease. Reduce heat to medium-low and stir in the corn, chili with beans, baked beans, tomato sauce and green chilies. Cover and simmer for 30 minutes, stirring occasionally.
